e as English/Japanese name\n|it=Luxio|itmeaning=Same as English/Japanese name\n|ko=럭시오 \'\'Leoksio\'\'|komeaning=Transliteration of Japanese name\n|zh_cmn=勒克貓 / 勒克貓 \'\'Lèkèmāo\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|勒克斯 \'\'lèkèsī\'\'|lux}} and {{tt|貓 \'\'māo\'\'|cat}}\n|zh_yue=勒克貓 \'\'Laahkhāakmāau\'\'|zh_yuemeaning=Same as Mandarin name\n}}\n<br clear="left">\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Clemont\'s Luxio]]\n* [[Rayler]]\n* [[Hareta\'s Luxio]]\n* [[Amp Plains tribes]]\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Electric}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Electric|prevnum=403|prev=Shinx|nextnum=405|next=Luxray}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Luxio]]\n[[es:Luxio]]\n[[fr:Luxio]]\n[[it:Luxio]]\n[[ja:ルクシオ]]\n[[zh:勒克猫]]'}